oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Image and autograph of DeWitt Clinton Senter
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Portrait of Conservative Republican and Tennessee governor (1867-1871), DeWitt Clinton Senter. Senter represented Grainger County, Tenn. In the Tennessee General Assembly and retired to Morristown, Tenn. Autograph note is written to "Miss Sallie" in 1887.
